y_pred_true = np.array([[[0, 1, 0], [0.32, 0.84, 0.73]], [[0, 1, 0], [0.66,

rankings = []
for y_pred_true_k in y_pred_true:
    rankings.append(rank_score(y_pred_true_k[0], y_pred_true_k[1]))
mrr_actual = mrr_score(rankings)
